<H3> <TI>   Talks Suspended; No New Date </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PA2102183994 Managua Radio Sandino in Spanish 1200 GMT 21 
Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA2102183994 </F>
<F P=104>  Managua Radio Sandino </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "Events" newscast] </F>
  [Text] The daily LA TRIBUNA reported this morning that the 
3-80 Northern Front, which was slated to discuss its disarmament 
with government representatives, has announced these talks have 
been suspended due to the strong presence of EPS [Sandinist 
People's Army] troops in the area of El Dorado. As yet, no date 
has been set for a new meeting between the rebels led by El 
Chacal [Jose Angel Talavera] and government representatives. 

</TEXT>

