<F P=100> Chile </F>
<H3> <TI>   3 Arrested After `Provocation' Near U.S. Embassy </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PY2202124694 Santiago Radio Cooperativa Network in Spanish 
1000 GMT 22 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> PY2202124694 </F>
<F P=104>  Santiago Radio Cooperativa Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Three individuals were injured this morning 
following a confusing incident near the U.S. Embassy, in the 
Parque Forestal area. 
  According to the first report, three individuals provoked 
Carabineros agents guarding the area and escaped when the agents 
tried to arrest them. Police organized a dragnet in the area 
with the support of central Santiago's Fourth Police Station. 
The individuals were finally captured and taken to the central 
hospital for the treatment of possible injuries. Police did not 
reveal the identity of the individuals in question, but we 
reiterate, their arrest was as the result of a provocation 
against personnel on guard near the U.S. Embassy. The incident 
occurred at approximately 0615 today. 

</TEXT>

