<H3> <TI>   Menem, Castro Reportedly Hold Telephone Conversation </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PY1802215494 Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS in Spanish 
1842 GMT 18 Feb 94 </F>

