occupation -- at least peaceful so far -- of the National Palace 
by government workers who belong to Fenasep [National Federation 
of Public Employees Unions]. The Fourth District judge was 
unable to enter the National Palace because of the crowd outside 
the building. Tight security measures have been implemented and 
