the five diplomats we mentioned in an earlier report who are 
inside the National Palace, the Paraguayan Ambassador Gilberto 
Caniza also finds himself trapped inside. These diplomats, 
along with those people who went to the National Palace today to 
carry out normal business and reporters who normally cover 
events at the palace, have been prevented from leaving. This is 
also true of officials who went to the Foreign Relations 
Ministry today to attend a diplomatic event that has been 
canceled in the wake of this situation. 

