made an effort in this area, but I believe it is up to Dr. Cesar 
Gaviria's administration to tighten its belt and see what sort 
of measures can be adopted on this final leg of the campaign to 
ensure protection. [end recording] 
  This concern has also been expressed in the past few hours 
by 
