<H3> <TI>   Senate Group Visits PRC; Commercial Offices Promised </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PY2202160594 Asuncion ULTIMA HORA in Spanish 21 Feb 94 p 7 </F>
<F P=103> PY2202160594 </F>
<F P=104>  Asuncion ULTIMA HORA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The delegation of Paraguayan senators visiting the 
PRC, headed by Carlos Alberto Gonzalez and made up of Antonia 
Nunez de Lopez, Diego Abente, Fernando Pfannl, Luis Guanes, 
Amado Yambay, and Arnaldo Rojas Sanchez, received the promise of 
